{"type": "article", "id": 1122, "title": "如果 iPad 壳上会显示消息……", "description": "根据美国专利与商标局（US Patent & Trademark Office）的消息，苹果申请一个带有消息显示功能外壳的专利。不过按照苹果历来的风格，这项专利最后会不会投产还真的不好说。", "date": "2014-06-13T10:23:21Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [{"id": 231, "name": "Apple"}, {"id": 382, "name": "iPad"}, {"id": 1117, "name": "外壳"}, {"id": 1118, "name": "专利"}, {"id": 68, "name": "苹果"}, {"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}], "category": 4, "author": 8, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160604215105QvUaPdOty7Lf13Nc.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t如果你有一台<span> iPad </span>，又担心自它的屏幕会被刮花，那么一般来说，你都是会考虑购买一块<span> iPad </span>专用外壳的。目前市场上主流外壳分两种，一种只具有简单的遮盖功能，另一种则是由如罗技等厂商澄清的一折叠键盘外壳。而根据<span><a href=\"http://appft.uspto.gov/netacgi/nph-Parser?Sect1=PTO2&amp;Sect2=HITOFF&amp;p=1&amp;u=%2Fnetahtml%2FPTO%2Fsearch-bool.html&amp;r=1&amp;f=G&amp;l=50&amp;co1=AND&amp;d=PG01&amp;s1=20140159867&amp;OS=20140159867&amp;RS=20140159867\">美国专利与商标局</a></span>（<span>US Patent\r\n&amp; Trademark Office</span>）的消息，苹果申请一个带有消息显示功能外壳的专利。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t通过使用多彩的<span> LED </span>灯光，这款<span> iPad </span>外壳能够在闹钟响起或者收到信息时亮起以提供消息提示，而它也将使用<span> iPad </span>的电源工作。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606042151039t286TrV7c5xIovG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604215104qsyBvIhAedmrcaR3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604215104g7Wf2AC8FLchZ0yl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t如果这项专利最终被投入使用，它将成为苹果生产的第一款不止拥有保护功能的外壳。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t当然，这并不是苹果第一次折腾<span> iPad </span>外壳。<span><a href=\"http://pdfaiw.uspto.gov/.aiw?docid=20140159867&amp;PageNum=9&amp;IDKey=6DD1C8E953E2&amp;HomeUrl=http://appft.uspto.gov/netacgi/nph-Parser?Sect1=PTO2%26Sect2=HITOFF%26p=1%26u=%2Fnetahtml%2FPTO%2Fsearch-bool.html%26r=1%26f=G%26l=50%26co1=AND%26d=PG01%26s1=20140159867%26OS=20140159867%26RS=20140159867\">2012\r\n年</a></span>，他们就申请了将外壳作为二级显示屏的专利，这项专利允许用户在外壳上查看下载的应用，并且将它直接作为键盘或者手写板。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t不过，申请专利并不意味着苹果就会出这样一款“智能”的<span> iPad </span>外壳。回望苹果历年的决策，它所<span><a href=\"http://www.patentlyapple.com/\">拥有的专利数</a></span>远远大于他最终问世的技术总量。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">题图来自 </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><a href=\"http://pdfaiw.uspto.gov/.aiw?docid=20140159867&amp;PageNum=9&amp;IDKey=6DD1C8E953E2&amp;HomeUrl=http://appft.uspto.gov/netacgi/nph-Parser?Sect1=PTO2%26Sect2=HITOFF%26p=1%26u=%2Fnetahtml%2FPTO%2Fsearch-bool.html%26r=1%26f=G%26l=50%26co1=AND%26d=PG01%26s1=20140159867%26OS=20140159867%26RS=20140159867\">US\r\nPatent &amp; Trademark Office</a></span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}